<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN205-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. kaṭiyaṉeṭuvēṭṭuvaṉ pariciṉīṭṭittāṉaip peruntalaiccāttaṉār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN205">
<l>muṟṟiya tiruviṉ mūva rāyiṉum</l>
<l>peṭpiṉ ṟītal yāmvēṇ ṭalamē</l>
<l>viṟaṟciṉan taṇinta viraiparip puravi</l>
<l>yuṟuvar celcār vākic ceṟuvar</l>
<l>tāḷuḷan taputta vāṇmiku tāṉai</l>
<l>veḷvī vēlik kōṭaip poruna</l>
<l>ciṟiyavum periyavum puḻaikeṭa vilaṅkiya</l>
<l>māṉkaṇan tolaicciya kaṭuvicaik katanāy</l>
<l>nōṉcilai vēṭṭuva nōyilai yākuka</l>
<l>vārkali yāṇart tarīiya kālvīḻttuk</l>
<l>kaṭalvayiṟ kuḻīiya vaṇṇalaṅ koṇmū</l>
<l>nīriṉṟu peyarā vāṅkut tērō</l>
<l>ṭoḷiṟumarup pēntiya cemmaṟ</l>
<l>kaḷiṟiṉṟu peyarala paricilar kaṭumpē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">Even though there are the Three of accomplished fortune, </l>
<l corresp="2">we don’t want [them] to give without desire. </l>
<l corresp="6">O fighter of mount Kōṭai with white-flowered hedges, </l>
<l corresp="5">with an army abounding in swords who destroyed the laborious minds </l>
<l corresp="4">of the enemies, there being a refuge to go to for those who have </l>
<l corresp="3">fast-moving horses when victory has cooled the anger, </l>
<l corresp="9ab">o hunter with a sturdy bow, </l>
<l corresp="8">with fierce, speedy, angry dogs that destroyed a herd of deer, </l>
<l corresp="7">whose loopholes, small or big, were blocked, </l>
<l corresp="9">  may you be without pain. </l>
<l corresp="14">The relatives of gift-seekers won’t return with bull elephants, </l>
<l corresp="13">majestic [beasts] who hold up [their] shining tusks, </l>
<l>along with chariots, who keep moving like majestic clouds</l>
<l>without water that had come together on the side of the sea (11f.)</l>
<l corresp="10">after the winds had made [them] descend in order to bring fertility with full bustle. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
